 better. \n\nYou must try! They get pretty busy on the weekends, so make a rsvp!", "Wow.  This is the best thai food i've ever had.  Every bite had so much flavor.  Garlic Prawn is a must-have.  Be prepared to wait if you don't have reservations :)"]
